title: [Caitria's Magic Shoppe]
[Caitria's Outfitting]
description: Glazed bamboo walls rise from a swirled sea glass floor.  Just above a braided seagrass rug hangs a silken sea-themed tapestry, and an etched seaglass ceiling completes the picture.  A bamboo rack and a shell-lined bamboo counter stand side by side in the middle of the room.
